# ── Data seeding (one-time, build-side only — NOT used at runtime) ──
# API-Football (api-sports.io) free key for the 2022 WC snapshot ingest.
# The seeder writes db/worldcup.db (committed); the app reads that file read-only.
API_FOOTBALL_KEY=

# ── LLM (NL → SQL) ──
# Default model for text-to-SQL. Provider is inferred from the prefix:
#   gemini-* → Google (free API keys from Google AI Studio — the demo default)
#   claude-* → Anthropic · gpt-*/o1/o3 → OpenAI
# The user's own API key is supplied per-request via BYOK (browser-stored),
# never persisted server-side.
TEXT2SQL_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash
